52.1	Capsule_hotel	Capsule hotel	A capsule hotel kapuseru hoteru) is a type of hotel, developed in Japan, that features a large number of extremely small "rooms" (capsules) intended to provide cheap and basic overnight accommodation for guests not requiring the services offered by more conventional hotels.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6d/CapsuleHotel.jpg/300px-CapsuleHotel.jpg
